{
  "stem": "7455.4",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he's giving out birth certificates, like, from the church; and an arbeitskarte, a card that she is working; identification card, as a work pass for a card; and several documents, very convincing.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And she has to have-- the photograph has a stamp from the German kommandantur, which half is on the stamp, and half is on the document.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Nobody could have done it, so it's very convincing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father listened.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The next night when I came home, he said, how much?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What should I have to give?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, I will-- Laura does not look Jewish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't look Jewish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Maybe-- men, they are circumcised.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They could examine them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They could betray.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Somebody-- my father said, somebody should survive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We thought there'll be no Jews in Europe.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Somebody should survive to tell what was done to us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said-- he wants all the information I should give him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, Daddy, we lost everything from the fire.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We don't have anything to give.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And what you give to Mr.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE], a few things, when we'll be starving to survive?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You have to have that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said-- he was thinking somebody should survive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Find out.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Find out.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He wanted somebody to live.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and he-- before the war, my Laura joined a Zionist organization, [?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Hashomer ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Hatzair. ?] And then it was necessary to go to a Hachshara, they call it, because Palestine was a pioneer country where they were-- had to meet, farm, and develop the country.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they needed to learn trades and farming, so they all had Hachshara where they would go to other towns and work, and get experience.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Work for very little pay.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the farmers were glad to give them that employment, because they didn't pay that much.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
